commit.message:
Update assets

 - Added raw inforgraphics to assets
 - Updated README.md to include name of the game - "Press [Up] to Play!"

Update README.md

 - Updated README.md to reflect submission on Devpost for Hack Cambridge 101

Major Code Cleaning

 - Removed unnecessary files and folders
- Included documentation in main.js
- Removed unnecessary lines and archived comments in main.js
Added scores and lives and restart mechanic

Cleaning code and adding end screen

 - Transferred main code from index.html to main.js
 - Added end screen appear mechanic
 - Stopped enemies from spawning once end game screen appears

Enemy update

 - Enemies now spawn at various heights
- Enemies are not affected by gravity

Random Spawn Working

 - Random spawns work now
 - Added jetpack joyride mode

Cleaning up code

- Removed game crash when computer dies
- Replaced enemy spawn lines with function

Basic working game initialised

Creating basic working game:
 - Based off Phaser's initial tutorial
 - Single "player", "computer", and one bomb
 - Todo: figure how to spawn multiple enemies
